highlights.description: Renee shares her hopes of building a community with shared understanding.
Renee talks about trust with law enforcement and accountability.
Renee recounts a story that happened in her childhood in regards to bullying and racism.
Hannah discusses her concern about safety in Dane county.
Rachel displays her concerns about the on-going mental health issues in Dane County.
Kayla talks about her concerns for safety in Dane County for residents who are discriminated against.
Kayla notes her concern with racial prejudice in the community against her and her family
Renee notes the importance of using your voice and speaking out.
Hannah talks about a past event she was involved in that focusses on normalizing kindness.
